response.original_title: Toxic Tv Hip Hop Reporters Vol. III - Portugal
response.overview: Almost two hours of footage with some of the biggest names in the Portuguese rap scene of the 00's. Featuring Sam The Kid, Bambino, Ace, Kacetado, Dealema, Kronic, Bezegol, Regula, Telma, Cruzfader, SP.
